ing: 2 large sweet potatoes, peeled and diced
6 ounces green beans, cut into 1 inch pieces
des: "This soup is full of healthy antioxidants. A very hearty soup for a cold winter night! I serve it with hot garlic bread. If you are lucky enough to have leftovers, it's great the next day!"
ins: Heat oil in a soup pot over medium-high heat.  Saute onion, celery, Italian seasoning, salt and pepper until tender, about 5 minutes.  Stir in tomatoes, with the juice, broth, sweet potatoes, carrots, green beans and garlic.  Bring to a boil; reduce heat to low and simmer, stirring occasionally, until vegetables are tender, about 30 minutes.
